name: Inedible Coin
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
What is the project about?
Inedible is an anti mev protection token. 

What makes your project unique?
Nobody can get sandwiched when making buys, making the space safer. 

History of your project.
Started as a meme token but now being built out with the launch of our dex Inedible X

What’s next for your project?
The creation of Inedible X

What can your token be used for?
The #INEDIBLE token will, of course, function as a governance token for the DAO. Holders will have control over different settings of the protocol such as trading fees and supply requirements.
